Hello everyone,

We are pleased to invite you to the first Confab Session of the semester;
a closed room discussion on the topic E2CLife Career Fundaes 101E2
D  with
Mr. Deepak Mirza.

Date: 26th August
Time: 06:30pm
Venue: Conference room, 2nd floor, IC&SR Building

Abstract of the talk:
This interactive session mainly focuses on the importance of self esteem,
hard/smart work, philanthropy, charity, etc. It helps us to improve our
leadership skills and find an improved understanding of our individual role
and place in the world.

Bio of the speaker:
Mr. Deepak Mirza is an alumnus of IIT Delhi and has over 30 years of
experience in the IT industry. He is an angel Investor in Mayabimbham Media
Pvt Ltd., an animation studio, credited with launching IndiaE2s fi
rst full
length 3D Animation Movie and Pixen Technologies Pvt Ltd., a healthcare
imaging software solutions company. Furthermore Mr. Mirza is on the Board
of Dax Networks Limited and Cenza Technologies Pvt Ltd. Mr.Mirza loves
interacting with young minds and giving life career fundaes.

